《'''BLACKPINK：照亮天空'''》（{{lang-en|''BLACKPINK: Light Up the Sky''}}，风格化为''BLΛƆKPIИK: Light Up the Sky''）是由卡罗琳·徐执导的2020年纪录片，讲述了韩国女子流行音乐组合[[BLACKPINK|BLACKPINK]]从初入行到名声大噪的故事<ref name=pitchfork>{{cite web|last=Minsker|first=Evan|title=Netflix Announces BLACKPINK Documentary Light Up the Sky|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/netflix-announces-blackpink-documentary-light-up-the-sky/|website=Pitchfork Media|accessdate=2020-10-04|date=2020-09-09|archive-date=2020-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007200101/https://pitchfork.com/news/netflix-announces-blackpink-documentary-light-up-the-sky/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Murphy|first1=Chris|title=Blackpink: Light Up the Sky to Light Up Netflix This October|url=https://www.vulture.com/2020/09/k-pop-girl-group-blackpink-to-release-netflix-documentary.html|website=Vulture|accessdate=2020-10-04|date=2020-09-09|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003052347/https://www.vulture.com/2020/09/k-pop-girl-group-blackpink-to-release-netflix-documentary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。纪录片于BLACKPINK首张[[正规专辑|正规专辑]]《[[THE_ALBUM_(BLACKPINK專輯)|THE ALBUM]]》发行两个星期后的10月14日上线<ref name = nytimes>{{cite web|last1=Winkelman|first1=Natalie|title=Blackpink: Light Up the Sky to Light Up Netflix This October|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/14/movies/blackpink-light-up-the-sky-review.html|website=New York Times|accessdate=2020-10-14|date=2020-10-14|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121173144/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/14/movies/blackpink-light-up-the-sky-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是BLACKPINK首部纪录片、Netflix首部[[韩国流行音乐|韩国流行音乐]]题材原创节目<ref name=deadline>{{cite web|last=White|first=Peter|title=Netflix Explores K-Pop With Blackpink Documentary|url=https://deadline.com/2020/09/blackpink-k-pop-netflix-documentary-1234573254/|website=Deadline Hollywood|accessdate=2020-10-04|date=2020-09-08|archive-date=2020-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916184905/https://deadline.com/2020/09/blackpink-k-pop-netflix-documentary-1234573254/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==梗概==
影片全方位记录了BLACKPINK自2016年爆炸性出道以来的经历，中间穿插成员们的练习生生涯、日常点滴、幕后故事及专访，呈现她们为了成为韩流巨星所要面临的考验及困苦、组合首张正规专辑《[[THE_ALBUM_(BLACKPINK專輯)|THE ALBUM]]》的录制过程、成员Rosé即将面临的个人出道及2019年[[科切拉音乐节|科切拉音乐节]]上的一鸣惊人。

